{
  "stem": "23942.8",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was made to feel ashamed because the other children who knew English made you feel like you are something of a strange thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't converse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I couldn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I didn't know what was being said in class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They put me into the classes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It's like throwing somebody into the water and saying, sink or swim.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I had to swim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I had to try to swim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I didn't know what I was doing in class when the teacher was speaking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They even tried to put me a little higher not-- because they couldn't put me with the first graders, but-- but I didn't understand the work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And it took me years till I-- slowly, it came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But the arithmetic, I don't know if I ever caught up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I don't think I ever-- reading, because I liked reading.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So it-- I caught up more than some other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I read a great-- but arithmetic, I never caught up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "History, I caught up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I know enough of world, everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But the arithmetic came the hardest to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And that's what I feel inadequate till today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But somehow, I swam through it like you swim through the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I swam through it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I look back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I wouldn't want to go through this again for anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I wouldn't want to go through this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Believe me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was-- it wasn't-- it wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- because I explained to you what it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- the-- the-- the memory of my mother being killed was so terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, if it was-- if she would have died a normal death, I don't think it would have been so bad.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But because she died-- the way she died, there was no closure.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
